&lt;p&gt;Taking a page (or really, an …&lt;/p&gt;</summary><category term="new year"></category><category term="blog"></category></entry><entry><title>Summer of Data Science 2017: Wrap-up</title><link href="https://magsol.github.io/blog/2017/08/15/sods-2017-wrap-up/" rel="alternate"></link><published>2017-08-15T16:38:18-04:00</published><updated>2017-08-15T16:38:18-04:00</updated><author><name>Shannon Quinn</name></author><id>tag:magsol.github.io,2017-08-15:blog/2017/08/15/sods-2017-wrap-up/</id><summary type="html">&lt;h2&gt;tl;dr&lt;/h2&gt;
